waitUntilDeployed

public void waitUntilDeployed()
                       throws java.lang.Exception
Waits until this Job is deployed. This is detected by checking that there is a pool with the poolname of the job, which contains a location whose name starts with the name of the job description. Awful hack, since this means that ibis.location cannot be redefined, or at least only be redefined such that it starts with the name of the job description. TODO: Fix! But how? --Ceriel

Throws:
java.lang.Exception - in case an error occurs.
